      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Very hard to knock the form of MAJESTIC GA GA (6) who has won five of her last six starts up to Group 3 level, coming from a 50m handicap for third in a G2 in the other. Far too good at this venue last time and looks well placed to strike again. MY LIGHTNING MCQUEEN NZ (8) has been racing consistently with a string of top-four finishes in the city since scoring back-to-back wins at this venue. Finished in front of MAJESTIC GA GA when a close second in a G2 two back, albeit with an advantage at the handicap. Go well again. MRIYA DREAM (1) gets the ace draw and should be be respected after winning two of her last three starts, taking her strike rate at this circuit and distance to 50 per cent. YANKEE LOVER (9) draws on the back row but was solid when runner-up to Majestic Ga Ga last start and has won here before.",
